            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I have no suspicions that metadata of `vim._with` (`@class vim.context.mods`) should be fixed. We have simply `@field bo? table<string, any>`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/305012ea073267492e1d626a304c6993b0dfa145/runtime/lua/vim/shared.lua#L1161-L1162\r\n\r\nThe tests that failed for me on `make functionaltest` are probably not related to the change from #30659 (although I did not repeat them on clean master branch): all come from `tui_spec.lua` or `scrollback_spec.lua`. \r\n\r\n\r\n",
